Class Coordinates

java.lang.Object
polimi.ingsoft.server.model.boards.Coordinates
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Coordinates extends Object implements Serializable, Cloneable
Object that identifies each and every of a Board's positions, representing a board as a cartesian plane
